d":57,"title":7,"artist":8,"source":9,"url":58},"542058337","https://music.163.com/#/song?id=542058337",{"id":60,"title":7,"artist":8,"source":9,"url":61},"1958727599","https://music.163.com/#/song?id=1958727599",{"id":63,"title":7,"artist":8,"source":9,"url":64},"1818615632","https://music.163.com/#/song?id=1818615632",null,{"id":67,"title":68,"body":69,"categories":190,"date":192,"description":193,"draft":194,"extension":195,"hide-info":194,"image":196,"meta":197,"navigation":199,"path":200,"permalink":65,"published":65,"readingTime":201,"recommend":65,"references":65,"seo":206,"sitemap":207,"stem":208,"subtitle":209,"tags":210,"type":212,"updated":65,"__hash__":213},"content/posts/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input.md","在 CachyOS Handheld 下恢复 Steam Input 中文输入",{"type":70,"value":71,"toc":182},"minimark",[72,76,80,83,86,89,95,110,120,123,130,138,141,145,156,162,179],[73,74,75],"h2",{"id":75},"前言",[77,78,79],"p",{},"我个人目前在 Steamdeck LCD 上使用的系统并非 SteamOS，而是 CachyOS Handheld，它也是基于 Archlinux 发行的版本，支持 SteamOS 的大部分组件，但是相比 SteamOS 它更为自由一些，软件也是跟随 arch 滚动最新的。",[77,81,82],{},"它不限制系统分区只读，可以自由使用 pacman 和 aur 安装想要的程序。",[77,84,85],{},"不过它毕竟是“仿照” SteamOS 实现的，并且要追求最新组件，所以有些老顽固功能比如 X11 是用 Wayland 替代的，部分应用也不附带，所以经典困扰 Linux 用户的输入法问题又出现了。",[73,87,88],{"id":88},"安装组件",[90,91,92],"alert",{},[77,93,94],{},"只恢复了游戏桌面下的游戏内 Steam Input 输入，且需要强制降级部分组件，请注意！",[77,96,97,98,102,103,106,107],{},"安装",[99,100,101],"code",{"code":101},"ibus","和",[99,104,105],{"code":105},"ibus-pinyin","以及",[99,108,109],{"code":109},"ibus-anthy",[111,112,118],"pre",{"className":113,"code":115,"language":116,"meta":117},[114],"language-bash","paru -S ibus ibus-pinyin ibus-anthy\n","bash","",[99,119,115],{"__ignoreMap":117},[73,121,122],{"id":122},"修改文件",[77,124,125,126,129],{},"打开",[99,127,128],{"code":128},"/usr/share/gamescope-session-plus/gamescope-session-plus","，找到以下行并修改：",[111,131,136],{"className":132,"code":134,"language":135,"meta":117},[133],"language-shell","# Input method support if present\nif command -v /usr/bin/ibus-daemon >/dev/null; then\n\t/usr/bin/ibus-daemon -d -r --panel=disable --emoji-extension=disable # [!code --]\n\t/usr/bin/ibus-daemon -d -r --panel=/usr/lib/kimpanel-ibus-panel --emoji-extension=disable # [!code ++]\nfi\n","shell",[99,137,134],{"__ignoreMap":117},[77,139,140],{},"重启设备，进入游戏桌面后添加中文键盘即可。",[73,142,144],{"id":143},"输入数字","输入数字？",[77,146,147,148,151,152,155],{},"如果你不降级",[99,149,150],{"code":150},"libxkbcommon","组件，会出现中文输入候选输入后为数字的情况，我们可以使用",[99,153,154],{"code":154},"downgrade","组件来帮助我们快速便捷的降级。",[111,157,160],{"className":158,"code":159,"language":135,"meta":117},[133],"# 安装 downgrade 组件\nparu -S downgrade\n# 降级 libxkbcommon 组件\nsudo downgrade libxkbcommon\n",[99,161,159],{"__ignoreMap":117},[77,163,164,165,167,168,171,172,175,176],{},"稍等片刻，就会出现组件版本列表，我们选择",[99,166,150],{"code":150},"的",[99,169,170],{"code":170},"1.11.0","版本，安装完成后还会提示你是否需要把包加入到",[99,173,174],{"code":174},"IgnorePkg","（后续升级也忽略），我们选择",[99,177,178],{"code":178},"y",[77,180,181],{},"等待降级完成后重启设备，再次尝试应该就是中文了。",{"title":117,"searchDepth":183,"depth":183,"links":184},4,[185,187,188,189],{"id":75,"depth":186,"text":75},2,{"id":88,"depth":186,"text":88},{"id":122,"depth":186,"text":122},{"id":143,"depth":186,"text":144},[191],"技术探索","2025-11-24T01:00:00","本文介绍了在 CachyOS Handheld 系统上恢复 Steam Input 中文输入的解决方案。主要步骤包括安装 `ibus`、`ibus-pinyin` 和 `ibus-anthy` 输入法组件，修改 `/usr/share/gamescope-session-plus/gamescope-session-plus` 配置文件，并降级 `libxkbcommon` 组件至 1.11.0 版本以解决中文输入显示为数字的问题。",false,"md","https://cachyos.org/_astro/handheld.DYNjpH4Q_1Y4Eos.webp",{"slots":198},{},true,"/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input",{"text":202,"minutes":203,"time":204,"words":205},"3 min read",2.035,122100,407,{"title":68,"description":193},{"loc":200},"posts/2025/11/cachyos-handheld-chinese-input","Arch 是最好用的 Linux 发行版？",[211],"Linux","tech","CuLSfie9Tz3q0QuOhtFxyAVoQo6Oi_jdYLB3pui-4EE",[215,220],{"title":216,"path":217,"stem":218,"date":219,"type":212,"children":-1},"Fedora Cosmic desktop Beta 一日游","/2025/11/fedora-cosmic-beta","posts/2025/11/fedora-cosmic-beta","2025-11-13T20:00:00",{"title":221,"path":222,"stem":223,"date":224,"type":225,"children":-1},"Riddle Joker：剧情不足，人设也不足","/2025/11/riddle-joker","posts/2025/11/riddle-joker","2025-11-24T21:00:00","story",1773069187857]